Global Orthodontic Treatment Aligner Market Insights
Orthodontic Treatment Aligner Market size was valued at USD 3.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 7.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Orthodontic Treatment Aligner Market Overview
The global orthodontic treatment aligner market was valued at approximately $2.3 billion in 2023 and is projected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 17.6% during the forecast period from 2024 to 2030. The increasing preference for aesthetically appealing dental treatments, along with advancements in technology such as 3D printing and digital imaging, is driving this market’s expansion. Moreover, the rising awareness of dental aesthetics and growing disposable incomes are further contributing to the adoption of aligners. The market is expected to continue expanding as more people seek alternatives to traditional braces for orthodontic correction.

